lead_paragraph: Patrick Mullins scored three goals, Patrick Nyarko had a goal and two assists and D.C. United beat the 10-man Chicago Fire 6-2 on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Mullins Has Hat Trick, United Routs 10-Man Fire 6-2
